# Dockdockgo

Dockdockgo is a simple multistage Dockerfile generator for distroless Go projects.

## Installation

```bash
go install github.com/bcarnazzi/dockdockgo@latest
```

## Usage

```bash
# generate Dockerfile
dockdockgo

# generate Dockerfile and expose 8080 port
dockdockgo -p 8080

# get help
dockdockgo -h
```

